
Spark will run on 3 modes..
  Local Mode
  pseudo Mode
  Distributed Mode
  
Local Mode:
============
This mode is used to check or verify application logic
Local mode works on standalone scala application

Pseudo Mode:
============
In this mode, spark will be running on single JVM

Distributed Mode:
=================
In this mode, N-workers & one master and one node per worker( single worker per node )
Spark will be running on cluster of machines..
